### Регистрация ROLE_USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signUp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nikita",
  "fio": "Никита Иванов",
  "password": "secret123",
  "passwordConfirm": "secret123",
  "role": "USER"
}

